# System volume controls
XF86AudioMute			:Exec amixer -q set Master toggle
XF86AudioRaiseVolume		:Exec amixer -q set Master 2+
XF86AudioLowerVolume		:Exec amixer -q set Master 2-
Mod1 XF86AudioRaiseVolume	:Exec amixer -q set PCM 2+
Mod1 XF86AudioLowerVolume	:Exec amixer -q set PCM 2-
